snippet.title: SOUTH PARK: SNOW DAY! | Collectors Edition Reveal
snippet.description:
Prepare for a blizzard of epic proportions with the SOUTH PARK: SNOW DAY! Collectors Edition available for pre-order now at www.SouthParkSnowDay.com.

Keep warm with Cartman’s Knit Beanie, enjoy your bathroom time with the Cartman Talking Toilet Paper Holder, or get into the holiday spirit with the Cartman Snow Globe. The Collector’s Edition also includes a select set of tarot cards, the original soundtrack, and the game SOUTH PARK: SNOW DAY! on the platform of your choice.
